<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<div style="min-width:100%!important;max-width:100%!important;width:100%!important;margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f0f0f0">
<center style="background-color:#f0f0f0;margin:0;padding:0;max-width:100%!important;width:100%!important;min-width:100%!important">
<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:600px;max-width:600px;min-width:600px;margin:0;padding:0" width="625">
	
		<tr>
			<td style="padding-bottom:0px;background-color:#f0f0f0" valign="top">
			<table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
				
					<tr>
						<td align="left" style="padding:0 50px 50px 50px;margin:0;text-align:left;font-family:'Arial';font-size:15px;color:#333;line-height:150%" valign="top">
						<p style="margin-top:30px;">Case {{{Case.CaseNumber}}}, created on {{{Case.CreatedDate}}}<br />
						{{{Case.Subject}}}</p>

						<hr />
						<p>Hi <strong>{{{Recipient.FirstName}}}</strong>,</p>

						<p>This is just a quick note to ensure we clearly answered your request with our last email. If not, please let us know so that we may further assist you.</p>

						<p>Thank you<br />
						{{{Case.OwnerFirstName}}}<br />
						<strong>The Brightcove Customer Support Team</strong></p>

						<p style="font-family:'Arial';font-size:15px;color:#000000">You can see all of your cases in our <a href="https://supportportal.brightcove.com/" style="color:#000000">Support Portal</a>, and current system status is always available on our <a href="https://status.brightcove.com/" style="color:#000000">Status Page</a>.</p>

						<hr />
						<p style="font-family:'Arial';font-size:15px;color:#000000">Our last response on {{{Case.Last_Email_Sent__c}}}:<br />
						{{{Case.E2CP__Most_Recent_Public_Comment__c}}}<br />
						{{{Case.E2CP__HistoryText__c}}}<br />
						<br />
						{{{Case.E2CP__Case_Thread_Id__c}}}</p>
						</td>
					</tr>
				
			</table>
			</td>
		</tr>
	
</table>
</center>
</div>
</body>
</html>